||
|c) latexmath:[$B \setminus A$]
|d) latexmath:[$B \setminus C$]
|======================

*Soluções:*

[width="100%",cols="<,<",frame="none",grid="none"]
|======================
|a) latexmath:[$\complement_B^A$]*latexmath:[$= B-A = \{ 1,3,5 \}$]*
|b) latexmath:[$\complement_B^C$]*latexmath:[$= \mbox{ não definido, pois } C \not\subseteq B$]*
||
